":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:11:23.000Z","msg":"啊～～～啊啊丫啊啊啊～啊丫啊啊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:51:31.000Z","msg":"做乜播聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fea2f8ea29fc7c8a3d1f1bb367b2ec28c37ebe7e","tid":1215112,"uid":30791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:52:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oYf3MTpC6Zo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DoYf3MTpC6Zo&d=NXUP4IJ4la%2FJDnFlXEjtWBTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=38417e1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oYf3MTpC6Zo</a><br />\n<br />\n觀自在菩薩，行深般若波羅蜜多時，照見五蘊皆空，度一切苦厄。舍&shy;利子，色不異空，空&shy;不異色，色即是空，空即是色，受想行識，亦復&shy;如是。舍利子，是諸法空相， 不生不滅，不垢不淨，不增不減。是故空中無色，無受想行識，無眼&shy;耳鼻舌身意，無色聲&shy;香味觸法，無眼界，乃至無意識界，無無明，亦&shy;無無明盡，乃至無老死，亦無老死盡，無&shy;苦集滅道，無智亦無得，以&shy;無所得故。菩提薩埵，依般若波羅蜜多故，心無罣礙，無罣礙&shy;故，無&shy;有恐怖，遠離顛倒夢想，究竟涅槃。三世諸佛，依般若 波羅蜜多故，得阿耨多羅三藐三菩提。故知般若波羅蜜多，是大神咒&shy;，是大明咒，是無上&shy;咒，是無等等咒，能除一切苦，真實不虛。故說&shy;般若波羅蜜多咒。即說咒曰：揭諦揭諦，&shy;波羅揭諦，波羅僧揭諦，菩&shy;提薩婆訶。"},{"pid":"2bbe3c6b9967e2bfeb88fe669ce19e1ed0711d02","tid":1215112,"uid":59242,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:11:12.000Z","msg":"一陣叫埋佛祖黎見佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好大嘅官良"},{"pid":"fc94b415a821244b9afaf11929e871d79da6259c","tid":1215112,"uid":59242,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2bbe3c6b9967e2bfeb88fe669ce19e1ed0711d02","tid":1215112,"uid":59242,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:11:12.000Z","msg":"一陣叫埋佛祖黎見佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好大嘅官良"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:11:29.000Z","msg":"官威*"},{"pid":"e135b6a0bd9432b2fca1da0259d64fa12874e3c1","tid":1215112,"uid":36089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:13:34.000Z","msg":"推啦"},{"pid":"ff62e22cbb1fc725821570bf6b76ee12a4b234de","tid":1215112,"u